Transit Gateway:
For having transitive peering b/w thousands of VPC and on-premises, hub-and-spoke(star) connection.
Regional resources, can work cross-region
Share cross-account using Resource Access Manager(RAM)
You can peer Transit Gateways across regions
Route tables: limit which VPC can talk with other VPC.
Works with Direct connect Gateways, VPN connections

Supports IP MULTICAST(not supported by any other AWS Service).

Transit gateway: Site to Site VPN ECMP
ECMP: Equal-cost multi-path routing
Use Case: Create multiple Site to Site VPN connections to increase the bandwidth of your connection to AWS.
1VPN connection = 2 tunnels(Input and output).
